SUMMARY:HPO Downtown Summer Concert Series
LOCATION:Fringe Boulevard\, King William St (between James St N and Hughson
  St N)\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Hamilton Philharmonic Orchestra (Hamilton)\nGenre: Fre
 e Outdoor Events\, Family Programming\nThe Hamilton Philharmonic Orchestra
  has a 140-year history of making and celebrating music in all corners of 
 our city and we are proud to call downtown Hamilton our home. In summer 20
 26 we are thrilled to present a free\, bi-weekly concert series on King Wi
 lliam Street in the heart of downtown. Join us every second and fourth Wed
 nesday of June\, July and August at noon as we turn King William Street in
 to the perfect afternoon patio with HPO ensembles.\nGeneral Admission: FRE
 E\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/hpo-downtown-summer-concert-series/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/hpo-downtown-summer-concert-series/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
