LOCATION:The Westdale\, 1014 King St W\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: SJMD (Hamilton\, ON)\nContent warnings: Depictions of 
 family conflict\nGenre: Musical/Concert/Opera\, Family Programming\nBased 
 on the award-winning novel by Kit Pearson\, Awake and Dreaming follows The
 o\, a child living in poverty with her young\, irresponsible mother Rae in
  Vancouver. When Theo meets the seemingly perfect Kaldor family on the fer
 ry and desperately wishes she could be part of them. The magic that follow
 s teaches her about family\, stories\, and the beautiful imperfections of 
 life.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/awake-an
 d-dreaming/
