  Great White North
LOCATION:Mills Hardware\, 95 King St E\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Ghosts Are Everywhere (Hamilton/Toronto\, ON)\nContent
  warnings: Audience Participation\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\, Theatre—Dra
 ma\nTwo Victorian spiritualist sisters invite you to a seance. But what ha
 ppens when someone tries to expose their act as a sham just as the spirits
  make their first move? Comedians Carly Anna Billings (The Second City Tor
 onto) and Cecilia O'Grady will take you back in time. Part comedy\, part s
 care\, this 60-minute show created and performed by these 'hilarious hosts
 ' (Common Ground Arts\, Edmonton) is sure to deliver you a spine-tinglingl
 y silly spirit-filled story.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://h
 ftco.ca/events/a-seance-spectacular-with-the-mystical-medium-wolf-sisters-
 from-the-great-white-north/
