DESCRIPTION:Company: Claudia Pompeya (Cincinnati\, OH)\nContent warnings: A
 udience Participation\, Coarse Language\, None\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\, 
 Storytelling/Solo Show\nOne clown. Infinite mothers. The Mother is a solo 
 alt clown-comedy dream walk through absurdity\, grief\, and self-repair. S
 trange\, sweet\, intimate\, interactive\, and a little haunted\, Claudia P
 ompeya turns every mother you’ve known\, needed\, or imagined into what 
 the League of Cincinnati Theatres called “a fever dream\, but a really f
 unny one.”\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/t
 he-mother/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/the-mother/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
