 : Coarse Language\nGenre: Theatre—Comedy\nHave you ever watched a musica
 l and thought - what’s going on with those townspeople? Probably not. Bu
 t we’re here to show you! Townsperson #3 follows the chaotic\, dramatic 
 and absurd lives of two townspeople as their kingdom slowly freezes over. 
 Inspired by the meticulously detailed and rarely seen backstories that ens
 emble members create\, this is the unhinged comedic ode to musical theatre
  you didn’t know you needed. Please note: this is a play about a musical
 . There is no music. Because it’s a play.\nGeneral Admission: $14\nMore 
 info: https://hftco.ca/events/townsperson-3/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/townsperson-3/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
